{
  "stem": "26276.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But meanwhile, he took me to a stable, where they had the horses.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they gave me a big brush to brush down the horses.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But then they let me off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did not go to school any after that, no.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing that I can remember, really.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't follow everything through.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was, you know, 12 years old.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't pay any attention to that stuff much, unless what I saw with my own eyes, right in front of me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Our town was not too bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't have any pro-- progra-- no, what do they call it?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, there were-- there were anti-Semites there, but they didn't show it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There  were no pogroms or anything like this, no.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Until they started taking the Jews and ship them out to the working camps.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say probably maybe about half to three-quarters of a year when they started it off.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They-- one days they went out and they put plaques on the streets that anybody up to a certain age should assemble in the school buildings or gymnasium buildings.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mostly men.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And otherwise, you were going to be shot if you don't respond.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So everybody was running-- you know, like everybody was afraid.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's what they want you to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's what you had to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You had to follow them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because everybody was afraid, really, that they're going to shoot you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, nobody ever went through anything like this in their life before.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My family didn't have to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was mostly for the single people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So from there, they came over-- you know, one of the high-ranking Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they would pick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They just looked at you and say, out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] you out.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
